## Design System (bespoke MN outdoors — NOT portfolio palette)

| Token | Value | Use |
|-------|-------|-----|
| Navy | `#003865` | Header/nav bg, strong text, official MN brand |
| Forest green | `#2D5A3D` | Visited markers, success states |
| Gold | `#FFC845` | CTAs, "Mark Visited" button, visited badges — MN brand accent |
| Teal | `#008EAA` | Links, active states, lake-inspired accents |
| Cream | `#F5E1A4` | Card backgrounds, warm panels — official MN brand cream |
| Page bg | `#FAFAF2` | App background |
| Dark body text | `#1A2B1F` | Primary text |
| Muted gray | `#A8A8A0` | Unvisited markers, secondary labels |
| Visited pin | `#2D5A3D` fill, white pine SVG glyph |
| Unvisited pin | `#A8A8A0` fill, white outline pine glyph |
| Home pin | House SVG, `#003865` |
| Font: Display | Playfair Display 700 (park names, H1/H2) — Google Fonts |
| Font: Body | Inter 400/500/600 (UI, descriptions) — Google Fonts |
| Map tiles | CartoDB Voyager (muted, clean, outdoorsy) |
| Border radius | 8px cards, 16px drawers, 4px inputs |
| Mood | Earthy, adventurous, MN-branded; topographic texture on hero header |

