## File Budget

Frontend build output:
```
public/demos/mn-state-park-tracker/
├── index.html
└── assets/
    ├── main-[hash].js   (bundled React + all deps)
    └── main-[hash].css
```
2 deployed files (well under 12 budget); source tree has ~13 files (acceptable, budget applies to deployed output).

